    "Afterwards, we deploy the EvoLLM and evaluate its performance on the BBO tasks.",
    "Our results focus on the PaLM-XS model.",
    "Figure 9 demonstrates the effect of fine-tuning on four different tasks (Sphere and Rastrigin with 2 and 5 search dimensions).",
    "For all cases, we observe a small but robust performance increase after instruction-based fine-tuning.",
    "In almost all considered cases, the tuned LLM outperforms both the teacher algorithm and the non-tuned LLM."
